version_description: We are moving towards multiple day jobs! This release is largely under the hood stuff in preparation for the oncoming surge in jobs!
Stability Improvements and getting the app ready to get all of our workers background check before working their first shift.
Getting Ready For Checkin and Checkout and squashed a few bugs!
We present to you Check In and Check Out! Get paid faster by telling your Shift Lead that you made it!
We've upgraded our Stripe Connection. This keeps everything running smoothly until the big update!
Squashing a few bugs and improving the Stripe Setup Experience!
